  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  title: Market
  body: 'Trading takes place at the market. To place orders, you need to supply the
    market with your items to sell, or your silver to buy with.

    Merchants walk
    past the left edge of the map to supply the market, bringing your market stockpile
    towards the target amounts you set for each item.'
